'''2014年南納帕地震'''（{{lang|en|2014 South Napa earthquake|}}）是2014年8月24日上午3:20分（[[太平洋時區|PDT]]）發生在[[美利堅峽谷_(加利福尼亞州)|美利堅峽谷]]附近的地震，地震強度[[矩震級|矩震級]]6.0，震央在美利堅峽谷西北約{{convert|3.7|mi|km}}，靠近{{link-en|西納帕斷層|West Napa Fault}}<ref name="usgs">{{cite web | title = M6.0 - 6km NW of American Canyon, California | url = http://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/eventpage/nc72282711#summary | publisher = [[美國地質調查局|美國地質調查局]] | date = 2014-08-24 | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | language = en | archive-date = 2014-08-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140824125028/http://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/eventpage/nc72282711#summary | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="BBC-28918600">{{cite news | title = 美加州舊金山灣區發生6級地震近百人受傷 | publisher = [[BBC|BBC中文網]] | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/08/140824_us_quake.shtml | date = 2014-08-26 | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | language = zh-hant | archive-date = 2014-08-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140826030209/http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/08/140824_us_quake.shtml | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

這次地震是[[1989年洛馬普列塔地震|1989年洛馬普列塔地震]]以來襲擊[[舊金山灣區|舊金山灣區]]最嚴重的地震<ref name=cnn>{{cite news | first1 = Josh | last1 = Levs | first2 = Susanna | 4 =  | last2 = Capelouto | first3 = Joshua | last3 = Berlinger | title = Northern California earthquake is area's strongest in 25 years | publisher = [[CNN|CNN]] | url = http://www.cnn.com/2014/08/24/us/california-earthquake/ | date = 2014-08-24 | accessdate = 2014-08-25 | language = en | archive-date = 2014-08-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140825034535/http://www.cnn.com/2014/08/24/us/california-earthquake/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="reuters">{{cite news | first = Jim | last = Christie | title = Quake rocks California wine country, dozens injured | url = http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/08/24/us-usaearthquake-idUSKBN0GO0A520140824 | publisher = [[路透社|路透社]] | date = 2014-08-24 | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | language = en | archive-date = 2014-08-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140825221154/http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/08/24/us-usaearthquake-idUSKBN0GO0A520140824 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。這次地震除了對[[納帕縣|納帕郡]]南部造成重大災情和火警外，在鄰近[[索拉諾縣|索拉諾郡]]的[[瓦列霍_(加利福尼亞州)|瓦列霍市]]亦傳出災害。約200人在地震中受傷
<ref name=PD-NPB/>，約69,000戶停電<ref name="wsj 14:23 ET" />。一具實驗中的地震警告系統在地震前對[[地震學|地震學家]]發出警訊<ref name=cbs/>。

== 地震 ==
這次地震[[地震序列|主震]]強度為[[矩震級|矩震級]]6.0，地震深度10.7公里<ref name=usgs />。[[美國地質調查局|美國地質調查局]]估計約15,000人感受到劇烈搖晃，106,000人感受到非常強的搖晃，176,000人感受到強的搖晃，738,000感受到中等程度的搖晃<ref name="cnn"/>。地震持續時間依地點不同約10到20秒<ref name="latimes.lanow" />，且至少有五次規模2.6到3.6的[[地震序列|餘震]]<ref name="cnn" />，是1989年[[矩震級|矩震級]]6.9的洛馬普列塔地震以來[[舊金山灣區|灣區]]最大的地震<ref name = "latimes.lanow">{{cite news | first1 = Lee | last1 = Romney | first2 = Ryan | last2 = Parker | first3 = Christine | last3 = Mai-Duc | first4 = Lauren | last4 = Raab | title = After earthquake near Napa, up to 100 homes labeled unfit to enter | url = http://www.latimes.com/local/lanow/la-me-ln-quake-near-napa-jolts-bay-area-20140824-story.html | publisher = [[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]] | quote = The main quake damaged buildings, cut off power to tens of thousands, sparked fires, broke water mains, caused gas leaks, sent more than 120 people to a hospital and led Gov. Jerry Brown to declare a state of emergency. | date = 2014-08-24 | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | language = en | archive-date = 2014-08-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140826040331/http://www.latimes.com/local/lanow/la-me-ln-quake-near-napa-jolts-bay-area-20140824-story.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。
因地震造成的嚴重災和可能的餘震，[[加利福尼亞州州長|州長]][[傑瑞·布朗|傑瑞·布朗]]在地震後宣佈該州進入緊急狀態<ref name="wsj 14:23 ET">{{cite news | first1 = Alejandro | last1 = Lazo | first2 = Ana | last2 = Campoy | title = Recovery Efforts, Repairs Start in California After Earthquake | url = http://online.wsj.com/articles/6-0-earthquake-shakes-northern-california-1408882575 | publisher = [[華爾街日報|華爾街日報]] | date = 2014-08-24 | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | language = en | archive-date = 2014-08-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140825183155/http://online.wsj.com/articles/6-0-earthquake-shakes-northern-california-1408882575 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

=== 人員受傷 ===
約200名傷者在{{link-en|山谷皇后醫學中心|Queen of the Valley Medical Center (Napa, California)}}<ref name="PD-NPB">{{Cite news | first1 = Derek | last1 = Moore | first2 = Randi | last2 = Rossmann | title = Napa's people, buildings hit hard by 6.0 earthquake | url = http://www.pressdemocrat.com/home/2575107-181/napas-people-buildings-hit-hard | publisher = {{lang|en|The Press democrat}} | location = [[聖塔羅莎_(加利福尼亞州)|聖塔羅莎]] | quote = Queen of the Valley Medical Center in Napa treated about 200 people by Sunday evening, ... About 27,000 people in the city of Napa and 15,400 in the city of Sonoma lost power, according to PG&E. The outages affected 6,000 customers in west Santa Rosa due to wires down near Piner and Fulton roads, 3,300 customers in Rohnert Park and 4,800 in Sonoma. | date = 2014-08-24 | accessdate = 2014-08-26 | language = en | archive-date = 2014-08-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140825201156/http://www.pressdemocrat.com/home/2575107-181/napas-people-buildings-hit-hard | dead-url = no }}</ref>，13名傷者需留院觀察<ref name="kgo7 4:45 PDT" />，大部份受到建築物掉落殘骸造成的擦傷和撕裂傷<ref name="cnn" />；至少6人傷勢嚴重<ref name="kgo7 4:45 PDT">{{link-en|KGO-TV|KGO-TV}} report from Queen of the Valley Medical Center, 4:45 pm</ref>。

